  "title": "Class 3 Bus Driver (with BDVL)",
  "description": "<p>Job description:</p><p>- To support transport operations including daily school bus</p><p>- To ferry passengers safely on schedule</p><p>- To perform daily general vehicles checking and maintenance</p><p>- To upkeeping cleanliness and hygiene of assigned vehicles</p><p>- To follow traffic rules and safety procedures</p><p>- Dispatch vehicles to and fro for maintenance, inspection and other vehicles errands</p><p>- Administrative duties include maintaining vehicles logs, documentation</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Process an excellent teamwork attitude with strong passion and be committed to task assigned</p><p>- Possess Singapore Class 3 Driving license with good driving records, preferly with Class 4</p><p>- Possess valid Bus Driver Vocational License</p><p>- Some experience and knowledge of operating electric vehicles, buses and/or heavy vehicles</p><p>- Preferably stay in Yishun or possess own transport</p><p>- Familiar with Singapore Roads</p><p>- Start work with short notice or immediately prefer</p><p><br /></p><p>*Working day: Monday to Friday and occasional weekends.<br /><br />* Full time & Part time option</p><p>*Attractive rewards and flexible working hours</p><p>*Able to take school bus trip morning & noon</p><p><br /></p><p>No agent please.</p>",
